Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.04,0:00:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.60,0:00:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,As if being dragged down these stairs...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.72,0:00:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,he was taken away...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.24,0:00:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.56,0:00:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,My big brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.44,0:00:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.88,0:00:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He was known as the "Man of the Red Rose Mansion."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.20,0:00:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What was his name?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.36,0:00:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Franz Bonaparta.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.76,0:00:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Franz... Bonaparta...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.96,0:00:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I don't know if that was his real name or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.96,0:00:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,since he also had a pen name.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.96,0:00:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,A pen name?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.32,0:00:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He was also the author of a picture book.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.56,0:00:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.60,0:00:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.56,0:00:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,was reading a picture book in here, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.24,0:00:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone opened this door...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.96,0:00:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and came home...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.20,0:00:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,A picture book?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.32,0:01:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.08,0:01:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a very peculiar picture book.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.68,0:01:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The title was "The Monster Without\NA Name," or something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.24,0:01:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing here Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.48,0:01:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this... memory...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.40,0:01:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have been reading a picture book in here, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.80,0:01:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,the one who opened the door and came in...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.80,0:01:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.72,0:01:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm welcoming myself back home?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.40,0:01:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.92,0:03:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Jan Suk's mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.72,0:03:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mrs. Suk is in room 409.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.60,0:03:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, her memory seems to come and go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.36,0:03:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how she's doing today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.56,0:03:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Jan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.92,0:03:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that you, Jan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.04,0:03:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.84,0:04:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,My, what a pretty girl you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.72,0:04:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a friend of Jan's?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.12,0:04:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.64,0:04:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Such pretty flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.44,0:04:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll arrange them over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.68,0:04:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have to make sure Aunt Olga doesn't take them away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.20,0:04:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Aunt Olga always takes my things for herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.36,0:04:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Like yesterday, she took away my doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.84,0:04:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,She's such a mean person.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.72,0:04:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But she passed away over ten years ago, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.96,0:04:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.16,0:04:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You know a lot, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.80,0:04:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard a lot from Jan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.84,0:04:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.96,0:04:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Jan still at school?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.80,0:04:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.68,0:04:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.52,0:04:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He already graduated and became a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.92,0:04:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.20,0:04:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Jan is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.84,0:04:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You have nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.64,0:04:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You have very gentle eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.96,0:04:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Please talk about anything you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.24,0:05:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Like different stories you remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.40,0:05:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.08,0:05:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,katherina from next door is very stylish.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.52,0:05:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.20,0:05:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this is fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.04,0:05:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a long time since I've had this much fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.04,0:05:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.88,0:05:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have to thank you somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.80,0:05:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to thank me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.56,0:05:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to see the thing Jan left in your care.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.92,0:05:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing he left with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.60,0:05:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,A cassette tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.44,0:05:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.07,0:05:52.08,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(750,300)\pos(360,340)}The Scariest Thing
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.96,0:05:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would've thought you'd leave it with Suk's mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.72,0:05:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll wait here while you go get the\Ncassette tape and the documents.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.52,0:06:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,However, you're going to forget about your business deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.96,0:06:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That was our agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.40,0:06:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.36,0:06:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I said this had nothing to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.04,0:06:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The story you told about what happened\Nto you in the last ten years...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.04,0:06:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,However, if that cassette tape is the\Nkey to revealing the big picture...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.16,0:06:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,your innocence may be proven.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.32,0:06:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The same goes for you as well, Mr. Grimmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.04,0:06:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that I've been investigating\Nwhat 511 kinderheim was.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.68,0:06:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.80,0:06:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,even if everything is revealed...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.12,0:06:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,my life won't change at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.08,0:07:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys would like to visit Mr. Suk's mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.48,0:07:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,She seems to be doing very well today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.40,0:07:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.40,0:07:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess the conversation she had with her\Nprevious visitor did her a lot of good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.48,0:07:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,A visitor?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.56,0:07:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.00,0:07:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.84,0:07:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,A beautiful woman with long, blond hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.96,0:07:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The tape!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.24,0:07:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you guys actually came.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.28,0:07:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I was told you were coming soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.32,0:07:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is the tape?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.00,0:07:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The tape?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.44,0:07:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.24,0:07:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,How is Jan doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.16,0:07:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.84,0:07:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take me to the hospital he's in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.04,0:08:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Jan's in trouble, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.96,0:08:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now my head feels very clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.28,0:08:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The person who was just here woke me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.64,0:08:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But it might only be for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.32,0:08:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let me see Jan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.00,0:08:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I will take you to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.48,0:08:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,To the hospital where Jan Suk is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.84,0:08:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Grimmer...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.36,0:08:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We've struck a deal with the secret police.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.04,0:08:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you call me, Jan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.80,0:08:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing... serious... Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.40,0:09:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You tried to keep me from worrying again, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.44,0:09:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same as that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.08,0:09:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That time?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.48,0:09:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You fell from a tree when you were nine, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.76,0:09:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I was worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.72,0:09:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,you said nothing was wrong and that\Nyou were fine, and kept walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.08,0:09:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though your ankle was badly sprained...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.88,0:09:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, God...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.20,0:09:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't let me forget this child...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.32,0:09:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Jan is my child.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.48,0:09:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I forget many other things...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.52,0:09:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,please, God...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.60,0:09:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,please, just don't let me forget about Jan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.96,0:09:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then, let's go back to the other question.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.60,0:09:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is it that you're most afraid of?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.36,0:10:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The monster inside of me is getting bigger{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.56,0:10:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Chomp chomp.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.88,0:10:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Munch munch. Crunch crunch.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.28,0:10:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Gulp.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.72,0:10:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Chomp chomp.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.88,0:10:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Munch munch.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.16,0:10:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Crunch crunch. Gulp.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.28,0:10:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.28,0:10:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to hear any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.32,0:10:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you should listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.00,0:10:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The nephew you sent to 511 kinderheim...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.76,0:10:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,is the same as this drugged boy being interrogated!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.88,0:10:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You should know what they did to your nephew!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.72,0:10:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We must listen to what comes after this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.16,0:10:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What lies be beyond this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.00,0:10:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What I am most afraid of...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.32,0:10:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}is that...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.84,0:10:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll forget Anna.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.08,0:11:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because of all these strange experiments\Ndone on me every day....{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.52,0:11:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}my memories are disappearing.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.76,0:11:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.68,0:11:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}don't let me forget Anna.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.44,0:11:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In this whole world...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.96,0:11:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}there's only Anna and me.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.84,0:11:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please, just this one memory.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.40,0:11:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.88,0:11:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's as far as I'll let you listen.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.92,0:11:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.84,0:11:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the voice of a young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.28,0:11:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be that he deleted the old recording, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.72,0:11:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I finally understand now.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.76,0:11:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,he recorded over it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.64,0:11:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I finally understand after listening to this tape.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.48,0:11:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The person who came to visit Suk's mother recorded this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.72,0:11:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.32,0:11:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what Johan's voice sounds like now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.80,0:12:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I finally understand...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}where I need to go....{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.20,0:12:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dr. Tenma.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.52,0:12:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He took time off?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.00,0:12:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean the inspector?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.52,0:12:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe that someone as devoted\Nto work as he would do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.84,0:12:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard it's his first long vacation\Nsince he came to this station!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.04,0:12:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he didn't seem all that busy lately anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.64,0:12:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He was considered to be an elite detective of the BKA.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.68,0:12:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He probably worked too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.28,0:12:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he doesn't know when to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.56,0:12:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard his wife and daughter left him because of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.12,0:12:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So, where did the inspector say he's\Ngoing to spend his vacation?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.56,0:12:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He said Prague, in the Czech Republic, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.92,0:12:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if he even knows how to take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.94,0:12:46.28,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\an8}Prague (Czech Republic)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.28,0:13:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you decided?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.20,0:13:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.36,0:13:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.36,0:13:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No, wait, I'm on vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.16,0:13:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.64,0:13:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What brand is this beer?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.08,0:13:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the local Prazdroj.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.20,0:14:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You think the public will be satisfied\Nwith a report like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.40,0:14:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't even know the whereabouts\Nof Detective Suk yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.04,0:14:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of that, do you know what would happen\Nif we announced these half-assed results...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.28,0:14:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,about the former Czechoslovakian\Nsecret police connection.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.80,0:14:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be sitting ducks for the media!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.32,0:14:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But now that all the people\Nwho were involved are dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.00,0:14:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The current situation of the Czech\Npolice and the Prague station...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.48,0:14:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,can't be resolved by simply\Nusing the dead as scapegoats!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.72,0:14:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.92,0:14:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If you understand, then hurry up\Nand continue the investigation!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.92,0:14:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And track down Suk too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.44,0:14:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,On the double!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.88,0:14:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.84,0:14:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.92,0:14:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm, there is someone who would like to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.52,0:14:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't see anyone who doesn't have an appointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.48,0:14:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, I don't have time for that right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.64,0:14:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But, umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.56,0:14:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You're!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.44,0:15:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you surprised me, Inspector Lunge.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.00,0:15:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't seen each other since\Nlast year's Interpol conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.32,0:15:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The lecture you gave at the subcommittee\Nseminar was very interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.08,0:15:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to have interrupted you at a busy time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.56,0:15:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I had no idea you were over here on vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.96,0:15:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really envious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.04,0:15:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Under the circumstances,\NI can't even get a decent break...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.56,0:15:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems you have your hands full, Commissioner Nepela.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.48,0:15:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.28,0:15:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm at the point where I'd like to ask you\Nfor some advice, if you don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.16,0:15:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, the case is in absolute chaos right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.00,0:15:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The connection between the Prague police department\Nand the former Czechoslovakian secret police...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.96,0:15:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It all began when an inspector named Zeman...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.80,0:15:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,was found dead among members\Nof the former secret police.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.80,0:15:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,At the time, Inspector Zeman...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.60,0:16:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,was conducting an investigation into the murder\Nof the director of an unauthorized orphanage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.16,0:16:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We found out later, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.96,0:16:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,both Zeman and the murdered orphanage director...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.24,0:16:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,had ties to the secret police.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.56,0:16:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is the suspect?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.16,0:16:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,A man named Grimmer, who first discovered\Nthe bodies, has surfaced as a suspect, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.32,0:16:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,the children at the orphanage said\Nthey witnessed another person...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.08,0:16:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,leaving the scene of the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.28,0:16:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Another person?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.24,0:16:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,A blond beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.96,0:16:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,However, the case didn't end there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.00,0:16:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It got even bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.52,0:16:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The previous commissioner and two veteran detectives...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.64,0:16:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,were all killed with poisoned candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.64,0:16:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,They were also affiliated with the former\NCzechoslovakian secret police.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.72,0:16:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is the suspect for the poisonings?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.08,0:16:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A young detective named Suk who worked\Ndirectly under Inspector Zeman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.40,0:16:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Any proof?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.68,0:16:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have any proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.80,0:17:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But the two detectives with the special investigative\Ntask force who were watching Suk...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.68,0:17:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,were found shot to death in Suk's room!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.08,0:17:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.76,0:17:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So, where is this Detective Suk now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.16,0:17:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He is currently missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.72,0:17:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,All the circumstantial evidence points to Suk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.40,0:17:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.04,0:17:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't smell like a man who'd commit such a crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.64,0:17:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.20,0:17:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm, how do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.72,0:17:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I know of a very similar case.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.32,0:17:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Impressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.68,0:17:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though you're on vacation, that\Nhand of yours is still working.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.60,0:17:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The objective collecting of data, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.96,0:17:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And you also said something else at the lecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.00,0:17:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,By using that data...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.72,0:17:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,you can conduct the investigation from\Na completely subjective perspective.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.56,0:17:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, by becoming the killer himself, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.32,0:17:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.64,0:18:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If you were Suk what would you be thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.12,0:18:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Where would you be now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.48,0:18:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm terribly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.32,0:18:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But unfortunately, I'm on vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.08,0:18:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, I should be the one apologizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.40,0:18:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you like the city of Prague?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.60,0:18:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,For the most part, I've been visiting\Nsecondhand bookstores.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.00,0:18:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Secondhand bookstores?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.48,0:18:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you looking for something?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.28,0:18:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to thirteen stores already.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.32,0:18:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally found a copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.84,0:18:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is, the reason I came here today...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.08,0:18:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,was to see if you could translate this Czech text\Ninto German when you have some free time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.44,0:18:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, a picture book?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.44,0:18:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.56,0:18:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know you had such hobbies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.48,0:18:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't mind leaving this with me, I'll have\None of my men translate it by tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.88,0:18:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it for your child... no, grandchild?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.24,0:18:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, well... you could say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.44,0:18:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Suk is definitely innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.92,0:18:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,As his friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.20,0:18:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I firmly believe without a doubt that he is innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.92,0:19:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The police asked me tons of questions, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.68,0:19:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,there's nothing shady about him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.48,0:19:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're with the police, then please help him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.08,0:19:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll cooperate in any way possible to help him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.60,0:19:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, I'm on vacation right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.80,0:19:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't be of much help.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.36,0:19:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Was there anyone else he opened up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.72,0:19:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He was close to getting a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.84,0:19:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd only gotten as far as getting her name, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.80,0:19:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What was her name?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.24,0:19:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Anna...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.08,0:19:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right! Anna Liebert!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.96,0:19:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She had blond hair and was extremely pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.60,0:19:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He was really happy because he thought\Neverything was going well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.64,0:19:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Anna Liebert...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.52,0:19:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the twins who survived the homicide\Ninvolving a high official...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.44,0:19:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,who fled East Germany due to exile ten years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.59,0:20:01.05,Title,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Moravia Publishing Company
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.08,0:20:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think we have any left.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.80,0:20:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Emil Scherbe's "The Monster Without A Name"...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.48,0:20:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,was indeed one of our publications, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.40,0:20:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,if it was published during the old regime...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.84,0:20:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,that would've still been during the\Nprevious company president's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.16,0:20:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Emil Scherbe a pen name?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.24,0:20:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it probably was.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.72,0:20:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,There were several other pen names as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.56,0:20:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Something Bonaparta...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.92,0:20:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, Jakov Vyrobek.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.40,0:20:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,klaus Poppe and such...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.68,0:20:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,klaus Poppe's box is here, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.40,0:20:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What? I'm surprised you found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.72,0:20:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,May I open it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.24,0:20:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.60,0:20:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's probably just some old rough sketches anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.52,0:21:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,A pregnant woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.40,0:21:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.92,0:21:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,children were born.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.76,0:21:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,A girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.96,0:21:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Twins...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.52,0:21:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.24,0:21:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You were able to translate it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.76,0:21:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate this, Commissioner Nepela.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.60,0:21:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'd like to ask something, since it's been bothering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.12,0:21:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But could you please read the last page to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.16,0:21:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let me see....{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.00,0:21:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Even though he now had a name..."{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.72,0:21:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"there was no one left to call him by his name."{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.60,0:22:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Johan."{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.68,0:22:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"It is a wonderful name."{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.96,0:22:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What a curious picture book...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.24,0:22:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.44,0:22:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inspector Lunge, how about having\Ndinner with me sometime?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.44,0:22:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How long is your vacation going to be?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.08,0:22:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.36,0:22:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like coffee instead of beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.84,0:22:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it'll be a long vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.89,0:22:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes... Gazing at what is known now in this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.24,0:23:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes... Your eyes believe in kindness...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.58,0:23:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Make it home... to your land of harmony...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.02,0:23:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Make it home... to your land of purity...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.99,0:23:53.49,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(750,0)\pos(360,340)}The Cruelest Thing
